			   ==========================
			   Pinball System for TS-7200
			      Design Documentation
			   ==========================
				    cs452_08

1. Overview
===========

The Pinball system is based on the Pinball kernel, targets to provide a
real-time OS and associated services and API for userland programming.


2. Component Synoposis
======================

* Services
----------

- Name server

The name server provides these APIs:

RegisterAs
WhoIs

- Time server

The time server provides these APIs:

Time
Delay
DelayUntil


* Drivers
---------

- Clock driver